text: The Ambassador of Malaysia to the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan is the head of Malaysia's diplomatic mission to Jordan. The position has the rank and status of an Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary and is based in the Embassy of Malaysia, Amman. ==List of heads of mission== ===Chargés d'Affaires to Jordan=== {| class=wikitable !
